parameters:
The exploration of this large hole has hardly progressed.
There are troublesome monsters placed to defend it...

It's like looking at the gates of hell. I wonder how a hole
like this could have been created...

Are you going down there? Seriously...? My weapons were
completely useless, so I had to retreat.... You guys should
be careful too.

I might be able to handle a little bit of magic, but I'm not
that skilled... And also... um, it's a little scary.

There's something strange about this place. It's like
something is off, like it doesn't belong in this world...

I wonder what's at the bottom of the hole...? For some
reason, I couldn't start a fire.

If you're planning to go, be careful because you won't be
able to rest by a campfire.

There should have been an altar here dedicated to the earth
spirits... And yet suddenly there's such a huge hole...

It is possible for holes to form due to a decrease in
groundwater, but there are no underground water veins in
this area. Hmmm...

\SE[53]Ah, you made it back.... \SE[86]It's kind of
amazing... I feel relieved....

\SE[4]In the end... What was it all about? \SE[3]That
place...

\SE[74]I don't know even if I think about it.... \SE[3]We
were able to investigate, so let's leave the rest to the
experts....

\SE[0]For now, it's a relief that we're safe.... \!\SE[0]We
still don't know the whereabouts of the Spirits though....
Haaah!! Finally, I made it back!!
Um... Well, yeah...? Who? You guys?
Guh...!! What are you doing!! And, what's with this power!!!

\SE[17]Shut up!! I've been searching for you all this time!!
\SE[35]I've been searching for a trial that may or may not
exist!!

\SE[14]Look at this! \SE[17]I was forced to explore this
giant hole!!

\SE[16]I was sent to a messy world!! \!\SE[33]I had to fight
against squishy monsters!! \!\SE[16]It was tough!! \.I was
scared!! \!\SE[35]I was about to cry just a little bit!!

I'm sorry about that, but... It's not like it's my fault or
anything...

\SE[2]What is this giant hole...? Where is the trial of the
earth...?

As for that, I have no idea either... A week ago, while I
was taking a nap, suddenly there was a loud noise like
BOOM!! and I was sent flying like WHOOSH!!...
Finally made it back...! It seems like it took a while.
\SE[74]So even the Spirits don't know, huh...

By the way, are you the blue one perhaps the Adapted One?
How about trying the Trial of the Earth while you're at it?

\SE[17]Don't mess with me! I absolutely refuse!! \SE[15]I've
already worked hard enough today!! \SE[35]No matter what
happens, I won't work anymore!!

\SE[17]For your sake! I've put in so much effort up until
now!! \SE[15]Shouldn't you just give me your power
unconditionally at this point...!?

Huh? Isn't that a bit too greedy...!! Well, but... I do have
some responsibility for management as well...

Earlier, you had a good punch too... Well, whatever! Let's
go ahead and bestow my power upon you!

\SE[86]Is that true...!? \!\SE[68]What a nice person...!
\!\SE[19]Thank you... I might end up falling in love...!!

Y-You're quick to change... It's a little scary. What kind
of power do you want? From what I can see, it seems like
increasing your 'attack' or 'defense' would be a good idea.
Oh... You've come from an unexpected place.

\SE[2]I know that I don't have the talent for magic...
\!\SE[3]But when I see Lunaroa and Vega using magic, \.I
can't help but want it too...

I see... Well then! I swear on the name of the Earth Spirit
that I will choose a magic for you!!

\SE[17]Is that true...!! \SE[19]If that's the case, I would
be happy to receive an amazing ability that takes those two
years to learn in an instant...!
Alright... This should work...! Receive my power...!!
Vita learned the Earth Mother's Banquet!

Well, that's my power after all. Go ahead and rampage with
it!

\SE[18]Thank you... Earth Spirit...! \SE[18]This is
amazing...! We...!!

\SE[15]Hehe... It was tough, but... \SE[15]I'm glad I got to
see Vita's smile.

\SE[2]I've always been curious... Why don't you use earth
attribute magic? \SE[3]It's not like you're bad at it,
right?

\SE[5]Now that I think about it, I might not have seen it
before. \SE[3]I feel like I've seen fire and ice go boom!
quite a bit... \SE[3]But earth attribute magic, it's not
really that strong...?

\SE[6]N-No...! That's definitely not true. \SE[5]But, um...
Just a little...

\SE[38]Compared to other attributes... \SE[37]it's a bit...
plain, I guess...

\SE[74]If that child and the spirits were to hear that...
they would be very sad, wouldn't they...

\SE[22]I-It's not like I have any ill intentions or
anything...
